\c 14  
\s1 Creatures that were forbidden to be eaten  
\p
\v 1 “\w We|strong="H4191"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w who|strong="H3068"\w* belong \w to|strong="H4191"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w our|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*. \w So|strong="H3808"\w*, \w when|strong="H1121"\w* \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w die|strong="H4191"\w*, \w do|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w show|strong="H7760"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H7760"\w* \w are|strong="H1121"\w* grieving \w by|strong="H3068"\w* gashing/cutting \w yourselves|strong="H5869"\w* \w or|strong="H3808"\w* \w by|strong="H3068"\w* \w shaving|strong="H7144"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* hair \w on|strong="H7760"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* foreheads \add like the other people-groups do\add*.  
