\c 29  
\s1 The agreement made in Moab  
\p
\v 1 \w These|strong="H6213"\w* \w are|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Israelis \w were|strong="H3478"\w* required \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w keep|strong="H6213"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* agreement \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w making|strong="H6213"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w*. \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w*/\w I|strong="H4714"\w* commanded \w them|strong="H6213"\w* \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w keep|strong="H6213"\w* \w this|strong="H6213"\w* agreement \add when they/we were\add* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Moab region \add on the east side of the Jordan River\add*. \w This|strong="H6213"\w* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w in|strong="H3478"\w* addition \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* agreement \w that|strong="H7200"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w made|strong="H6213"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H6213"\w*/\w us|strong="H6213"\w* \w at|strong="H3478"\w* Sinai \add Mountain\add*.   
\p
\v 2 Moses/\w I|strong="H7200"\w* summoned \w all|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H7200"\w* \w and|strong="H1419"\w* said \w to|strong="H7200"\w* \w them|strong="H1992"\w*, “\w You|strong="H7200"\w* \w saw|strong="H7200"\w* [SYN] \w for|strong="H5869"\w* \w yourselves|strong="H5869"\w* \w what|strong="H7200"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w did|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H7200"\w* \w the|strong="H7200"\w* king \w of|strong="H5869"\w* Egypt \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w to|strong="H7200"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* officials \w and|strong="H1419"\w* \w to|strong="H7200"\w* \w his|strong="H7200"\w* entire country.  
