\v 5 \w For|strong="H3588"\w* 40 years \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w has|strong="H3068"\w* \w led|strong="H3068"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w while|strong="H3588"\w* \w you|strong="H3588"\w* \w traveled|strong="H3045"\w*/walked \w through|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* desert. During \w that|strong="H3588"\w* time, \w your|strong="H3068"\w* clothes \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w your|strong="H3068"\w* sandals \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* worn \w out|strong="H3045"\w*.  
